trans-unit.source: Defines an abstract base class for composable part definitions, which describe and enable the creation of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Definisce una classe base astratta per le definizioni di parte componibile, che descrivono e abilitano la creazione di <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"> </xref> oggetti.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inizializza una nuova istanza di <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of a part that the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> describes.
trans-unit.target: Crea una nuova istanza di una parte che il <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref> descrive.

trans-unit.source: Derived types that override this method should return a new instance of a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> object every time that the method is invoked and should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: I tipi derivati che eseguono l'override di questo metodo devono restituire una nuova istanza di un <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>oggetto ogni volta che il metodo viene richiamato e non deve mai restituire `null`.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition"></xref> objects that describe the objects exported by the part defined by this <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene una raccolta di <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition"> </xref> oggetti che descrivono gli oggetti esportati da una parte definita da questo <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref> oggetto.

trans-unit.source: Overrides of this property should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Esegue l'override di questa proprietà non devono restituire mai `null`.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> objects created by the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> do not provide exported objects, return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> collection instead.
trans-unit.target: Se il <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>degli oggetti creati dal <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition>non forniscono oggetti esportati, restituire un oggetto vuoto <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601>raccolta invece.</xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>

trans-unit.source: A collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition"></xref> objects that describe the exported objects provided by <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"></xref> objects created by the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Una raccolta di <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition"> </xref> oggetti che descrivono gli oggetti esportati forniti da <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"> </xref> degli oggetti creati dal <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition"></xref> objects that describe the imports required by the part defined by this <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene una raccolta di <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition"> </xref> oggetti che descrivono le importazioni richieste da una parte definita da questo <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref> oggetto.

trans-unit.source: Overrides of this property should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Esegue l'override di questa proprietà non devono restituire mai `null`.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> objects created by the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> do not have imports, return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> collection instead.
trans-unit.target: Se il <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>degli oggetti creati dal <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition>non dispongono di importazioni, restituire un oggetto vuoto <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601>raccolta invece.</xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>

trans-unit.source: A collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition"></xref> objects that describe the imports required by <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"></xref> objects created by the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Una raccolta di <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition"> </xref> oggetti che descrivono le importazioni richieste da <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"> </xref> degli oggetti creati dal <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of the metadata for this <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene una raccolta dei metadati per questo <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref> oggetto.

trans-unit.source: Overrides of this property should return a read-only <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> object with a case-sensitive, non-linguistic comparer, such as <xref:System.StringComparer.Ordinal%2A>, and should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Esegue l'override di questa proprietà devono restituire una sola lettura <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602>oggetto con un operatore di confronto non linguistico, distinzione maiuscole/minuscole, ad esempio <xref:System.StringComparer.Ordinal%2A>e non devono mai restituire `null`.</xref:System.StringComparer.Ordinal%2A> </xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> does not contain metadata, return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> object instead.
trans-unit.target: Se il <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition>non contengono i metadati, viene restituito un oggetto vuoto <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602>invece.</xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition>

trans-unit.source: A collection that contains the metadata for the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Una raccolta che contiene i metadati per il <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty, read-only <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> object.
trans-unit.target: Il valore predefinito è vuoto, sola lettura <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> oggetto.
